{
  "scene1_1_0": {
    "duration": 1.224,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene1/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "你敢相信吗"
  },
  "scene1_1_1": {
    "duration": 5.796,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene1/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "两张一模一样的数据图，一张看起来风平浪静，另一张却像世界末日"
  },
  "scene1_1_2": {
    "duration": 3.6,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene1/01_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这就是我们要聊的《统计素养》第三课：图表骗术"
  },
  "scene2_1_0": {
    "duration": 5.004,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene2/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "很多时候，同样的增长，只要换个坐标轴，就能把“毛毛雨”变成“大地震”"
  },
  "scene2_1_1": {
    "duration": 4.248,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene2/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这种把1%的差异硬生生画成断崖效果的手段"
  },
  "scene2_1_2": {
    "duration": 3.204,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene2/01_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "就是数据圈最经典的陷阱——截断坐标轴"
  },
  "scene3_1_0": {
    "duration": 1.656,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "不想被当成韭菜割"
  },
  "scene3_1_1": {
    "duration": 2.124,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "你要学会一套“图表审计法”"
  },
  "scene3_2_0": {
    "duration": 3.096,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "下次看到任何让你心跳加速的图表"
  },
  "scene3_2_1": {
    "duration": 2.16,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "先在心里问自己三个问题："
  },
  "scene3_2_2": {
    "duration": 2.556,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "第一，Y轴是从0开始的吗"
  },
  "scene3_2_3": {
    "duration": 2.844,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/02_正文_3.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 3,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "第二，时间范围是不是被“掐头去尾”了"
  },
  "scene3_2_4": {
    "duration": 2.664,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/02_正文_4.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 4,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "第三，比例有没有被刻意扭曲"
  },
  "scene3_3_0": {
    "duration": 2.016,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "永远记住这句万能金句："
  },
  "scene3_3_1": {
    "duration": 2.7,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene3/03_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "“这张图的坐标轴，到底有没有猫腻？”"
  },
  "scene4_1_0": {
    "duration": 2.556,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene4/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "我们来看第一种招数：樱桃采摘"
  },
  "scene4_2_0": {
    "duration": 4.068,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene4/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "比如你刷到一张理财广告，曲线一路狂飙，涨幅惊人"
  },
  "scene4_2_1": {
    "duration": 1.368,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene4/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "但你没看到的是"
  },
  "scene4_2_2": {
    "duration": 5.4,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene4/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "它可能隐藏了之前暴跌的半年，只截取了最近反弹的那三天给你看"
  },
  "scene4_2_3": {
    "duration": 1.368,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene4/02_正文_3.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 3,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这时候你得问："
  },
  "scene4_2_4": {
    "duration": 2.916,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene4/02_正文_4.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 4,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "“为什么只展示这段时间？之前的数据呢？”"
  },
  "scene5_1_0": {
    "duration": 2.952,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene5/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "第二种招数更花哨：3D幻觉"
  },
  "scene5_2_0": {
    "duration": 3.096,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene5/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "很多人喜欢用那种炫酷的3D饼图"
  },
  "scene5_2_1": {
    "duration": 2.448,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene5/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "但因为“近大远小”的透视原理"
  },
  "scene5_2_2": {
    "duration": 4.608,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene5/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "离你近的那块饼哪怕实际占比很小，视觉上也会显得巨大"
  },
  "scene5_2_3": {
    "duration": 0.972,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene5/02_正文_3.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 3,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "记住,"
  },
  "scene5_2_4": {
    "duration": 3.024,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene5/02_正文_4.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 4,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "越花哨的图表，越可能在掩盖事实"
  },
  "scene6_1_0": {
    "duration": 2.556,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene6/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "第三种是最损的：截断Y轴"
  },
  "scene6_2_0": {
    "duration": 6.408,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene6/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "比如某项指标从98涨到了99，如果坐标轴从0开始，这几乎是一条横线；"
  },
  "scene6_2_1": {
    "duration": 5.004,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene6/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "但如果坐标轴从95开始，这1%的增长看起来就像翻了一倍"
  },
  "scene6_2_2": {
    "duration": 4.212,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene6/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这种图专门欺负那些只看柱子高度、不看刻度数字的人"
  },
  "scene7_1_0": {
    "duration": 1.404,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene7/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "最后总结一下："
  },
  "scene7_1_1": {
    "duration": 3.024,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene7/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "图表本身不会说谎，但作图的人会"
  },
  "scene7_2_0": {
    "duration": 3.456,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene7/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "永远检查坐标轴、时间跨度和真实比例"
  },
  "scene7_2_1": {
    "duration": 3.816,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene7/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "当你学会审视图表的时候，数据才不敢对你撒谎"
  },
  "scene7_3_0": {
    "duration": 3.024,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_2/scene7/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "关注我，带你拆穿更多数据背后的真相"
  }
}